                        Sergius was decapitated at <span class="tei-placeName"><a href="http://syriaca.org/place/165">Resafa</a></span> on the <span class="tei-placeName"><a href="http://syriaca.org/place/82">Euphrates</a></span>.</span></div><div class="tei-note">
